are Maps\n✅ No runtime type checking overhead\n✅ More predictable and maintainable\n✅ Same performance characteristics\n\nLatest commit: b44b798\nCI is running...","createdAt":"2025-11-15T11:47:29Z","includesCreatedEdit":false,"isMinimized":false,"minimizedReason":"","reactionGroups":[],"url":"https://github.com/hyoo-ru/mam_mol/pull/807#issuecomment-3536410038","viewerDidAuthor":true},{"id":"IC_kwDOA3vPgs7SyWny","author":{"login":"konard"},"authorAssociation":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"## ✅ All CI Checks Passing\n\nAll 22 CI workflows have completed successfully! ✅\n\nThe polymorphism has been eliminated from both dictionary trees:\n- ✅ `riches` tree (type registration)\n- ✅ `shapes` tree (POJO serialization)\n\nAll tree nodes are now consistently `Map` objects with terminal values stored under the `$mol_vary_tree_value` Symbol key.\n\n**Key improvements:**\n- No more polymorphism (no mixing Map/function or Map/array types)\n- No runtime type checks needed\n- Cleaner, more maintainable code\n- All existing functionality preserved\n\nReady for review!","createdAt":"2025-11-15T11:54:10Z","includesCreatedEdit":false,"isMinimized":false,"minimizedReason":"","reactionGroups":[],"url":"https://github.com/hyoo-ru/mam_mol/pull/807#issuecomment-3536415218","viewerDidAuthor":true},{"id":"IC_kwDOA3vPgs7SyWsz","author":{"login":"konard"},"authorAssociation":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"## 🤖 Solution Draft Log\nThis log file contains the complete execution trace of the AI solution draft process.\n\n💰 **Cost estimation:**\n- Public pricing estimate: $2.011047 USD\n- Calculated by Anthropic: $1.025229 USD\n- Difference: $-0.985818 (-49.02%)\n📎 **Log file uploaded as GitHub Gist** (248KB)\n🔗 [View complete solution draft log](https://gist.github.com/konard/bdb1bcd5174209f02c5b9d06b3677a24)\n---\n*Now working session is ended, feel free to review and add any feedback on the solution draft.*","createdAt":"2025-11-15T11:54:42Z","includesCreatedEdit":false,"isMinimized":false,"minimizedReason":"",