{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","is_bot":false,"login":"konard","name":"Konstantin Diachenko"},"body":"## Summary\n\nThis PR adds comprehensive edge case tests for `$mol_vary` to improve test coverage and ensure robust handling of boundary conditions and special values.\n\nFixes #800\n\n## Changes\n\nAdded missing test cases across multiple categories:\n\n### Special Numeric Values\n- **Special floats**: `NaN`, `Infinity`, `-Infinity`, `-0`\n- **Boundary values**: exact boundaries between encoding sizes (27/28, 255/256, 65535/65536, etc.)\n\n### Empty Collections\n- Empty string (`\"\"`)\n- Empty arrays (`[]`)\n- Empty objects (`{}`)\n- Empty `Map`\n- Empty `Set`\n- Empty typed arrays\n\n### Unicode Support\n- Emojis: `🎉`\n- Multibyte characters: `你好`\n- Multiple emojis: `🔥✨💡`\n\n### TypedArray Coverage\n- Added missing `Uint16Array` and `Int16Array` tests\n- Empty typed array tests\n\n### Complex Structures\n- Deeply nested arrays (4 levels deep)\n- Mixed type lists containing various data types\n- Nested mixed structures with objects and arrays\n\n## Test Coverage Summary\n\nThe test suite now covers:\n- ✅ All logical values (null, true, false, undefined)\n- ✅ Special float values (NaN, Infinity, -Infinity, -0)\n- ✅ Unsigned integers (all size ranges: inline, 1/2/4/8 bytes)\n- ✅ Signed integers (all size ranges)\n- ✅ Regular floats\n- ✅ Empty and non-empty strings\n- ✅ Unicode strings\n- ✅ All typed arrays including Uint16Array/Int16Array\n- ✅ Empty typed arrays\n- ✅ Lists (empty, simple, nested, with deduplication)\n- ✅ Objects (empty, simple, nested, with deduplication)\n- ✅ Native Map (empty and with data)\n- ✅ Native Set (empty and with data)\n- ✅ Native Date\n- ✅ Custom classes\n- ✅ Complex nested structures\n- ✅ Boundary values for all integer encoding sizes\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)","closedAt":"2025-11-11T12:56:44Z","comments":[{"id":"IC_kwDOA3vPgs7RUOFk","author":{"login":"konard"},"authorAssociation":"CONTRI