{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","is_bot":false,"login":"konard","name":"Konstantin Diachenko"},"body":"## Summary\nThis PR modifies `$mol_attach` to use `$mol_gallery` for its layout, as requested by maintainer feedback. This enables the attachment component to leverage the gallery's responsive layout capabilities.\n\n## Changes Made\n- **Modified $mol_attach**: Changed the Content component from `$mol_row` to `$mol_gallery`\n- **Updated property binding**: Changed from `sub` to `items` to match `$mol_gallery`'s interface\n- **Kept $mol_gallery unchanged**: No modifications to the gallery component itself\n- **Added test script**: Created an experiment script to verify gallery behavior with multiple items\n\n## Implementation Details\n### `attach/attach.view.tree`\n- Changed `Content $mol_row` to `Content $mol_gallery`\n- Updated property from `sub <= content` to `items <= content`\n\n### Benefits\n- $mol_attach now inherits $mol_gallery's responsive layout behavior\n- Automatically splits items into two columns when more than 3 items are present\n- Maintains all existing $mol_attach functionality (file upload, item removal)\n\n## Testing\nCreated `experiments/test_attach_gallery.view.tree` to verify the gallery behavior with 5 test items, confirming the two-column split functionality works as expected.\n\nFixes #464\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)","closedAt":null,"comments":[{"id":"IC_kwDOA3vPgs7HT-Jd","author":{"login":"konard"},"authorAssociation":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"## 🤖 Solution Draft Log\n\nThis log file contains the complete execution trace of the AI solution draft process.\n\n📎 **Log file uploaded as GitHub Gist** (178KB)\n🔗 [View complete solution draft log](https://gist.github.com/konard/dd2313910e726fe606a77f97ebd393d2)\n\n---\n*Log automatically attached by solve.mjs with --attach-logs option*","createdAt":"2025-09-28T17:12:57Z","includesCreatedEdit":false,"isMinimized":false,"minimizedReason":"","reactionGroups":[],"u