=== PR #783 ===
{"author":{"id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","is_bot":false,"login":"konard","name":"Konstantin Diachenko"},"body":"## 📋 Issue Reference\nFixes #739\n\n## 🔍 Problem Analysis\n\nThe issue occurred when a parent `$mol_mem` was restarted/invalidated, causing `$mol_wire_sync` to be re-executed with new parameters. The problem was in `wire/task/task.ts` in the `$mol_wire_task.getter()` function:\n\n1. When a task is called via `$mol_wire_sync`, a `$mol_wire_task` fiber is created\n2. When the parent mem changes (e.g., filter changes from \"12\" to \"123\"), the task is restarted\n3. The old task with its promise (containing a destructor) was abandoned without calling its destructor\n4. This prevented cleanup code (like aborting fetch requests) from running\n\n## 🔧 Solution\n\nAdded a call to `existen.destructor()` when a task cannot be reused due to changed parameters (task/host/args). This ensures that:\n\n- Promise destructors are properly called when a task is replaced\n- Resources are cleaned up before creating a new task\n- The \"fetch aborted\" message is logged as expected in the reproduction case\n\n## 📝 Changes Made\n\n**File: `wire/task/task.ts`**\n- Added `existen.destructor()` call when replacing an existing task with a new one\n- Removed obsolete comment about non-idempotency\n\n## ✅ Testing\n\nThe fix addresses the reproduction cases from the issue:\n- When filter changes from \"12\" to \"123\" after 100ms, the destructor is now called on the first promise\n- The \"fetch aborted\" message now appears in console as expected\n- No breaking changes to existing functionality\n\n## 📚 Technical Details\n\nThe fix is minimal and targeted:\n- Only affects the case where a task is being replaced (different args/host/task)\n- Destructor is called before the warning log, ensuring proper cleanup order\n- Works with the existing fiber lifecycle management\n\n---\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)","closedAt":null,"comments":[{"id":"IC_kwDOA3vPgs7HMYlm","author":{"login":"konard"},"authorAssociation":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"## 🤖 Solution Draft Log\n\nThis log file contains the complete execution trace of the AI solution draft process.\n\n📎 **Log file uploaded as GitHub Gist** (217KB)\n🔗 [View complete solution draft log](https://gist.github.com/konard/922260d65b07da0a01217db8cb6091d2)\n\n---\n*Log automatically attached by solve.mjs with --attach-logs option*","createdAt":"2025-09-27T16:46:48Z","includesCreatedEdit":false,"isMinimized":false,"minimizedReason":"","reactionGroups":[],"url":"https://github.com/hyoo-ru/mam_mol/pull/783#issuecomment-3341912422","viewerDidAuthor":true}],"createdAt":"2025-09-27T16:42:15Z","mergedAt":null,"reviews":[],"state":"OPEN","title":"Не работает деструктор в экшене при перезапуске родительского mem-а"}

